# 🍴 Tikim Diaries: A Filipino Recipe Book

**Tikim Diaries** is a modern, responsive web-based recipe book that celebrates the rich and diverse culinary traditions of the Philippines. It features beautifully styled recipe cards, dynamic layouts, and a mobile-friendly design built with **Tailwind CSS**.

